# Ignore everything by default
*

# Whitelist the essentials
!.gitignore
!.SRCINFO
!PKGBUILD

# Whitelist auxiliary files
!*.install
!*.patch
!*.diff
!*.service
!*.desktop
!*.conf
!*.png
!*.svg
!*.sysusers
!*.tmpfiles
!LICENSE
!README.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!*.ini
!*.txt

# Package-specific files
!ChangeLog
